        "Finalization",
        "2025-01-01"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我先确认一下结构：Planning阶段包含项目启动和架构设计，Core Development聚焦数据库和认证体系，Feature Development做内容、任务和消息模块，Finalization收尾测试和上线。时间跨度大概到2025年7月中旬，这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Project Setup",
        "Architecture Design",
        "Database Implementation",
        "Authentication System",
        "Testing & QA",
        "Deployment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但Core Development里还需要加上用户管理和团队管理，这两个模块在认证之后做，各两周。Feature Development的时间线也要往后顺延。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Management",
        "Team Management",
        "Core Development",
        "Authentication System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把用户管理和团队管理插到认证系统后面，每个任务两周，认证2月22日开始，用户管理3月8日，团队管理3月22日。现在核心开发这块从数据库到团队管理形成了连续六周的链条。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Database Implementation",
        "Authentication System",
        "User Management",
        "Team Management",
        "2025-02-01",
        "2025-03-22"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Feature Development部分，内容管理需要三周，任务管理三周，消息系统两周。内容管理从4月5日开始。另外Finalization阶段要有测试QA三周、部署一周，最后是培训和文档两周。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Content Management",
        "Task Management",
        "Messaging System",
        "Testing & QA",
        "Deployment",
        "Training & Documentation",
        "2025-04-05",
